data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on an expansive 9.02-acre lot that offers both tranquility and endless possibilities. This stunning 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath home boasts breathtaking views from every room, providing a constant connection to the beauty of nature. The 2 detached workshops with water and power connections are perfect for any types of projects or workspaces. And solar panels are owner owned! New well, upgraded 400amps panel box,  newly painted exterior and new carpet. This property offers the ultimate privacy. You can relax on the private balcony and enjoy the gorgeous view & nature that surrounds you. Don't miss this rare opportunity!  Public record showed  2,462 SqFt plus approx 1,700 Sq Ft finished  basement area not permitted.
